{"tid":7072,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"你地主人會唔會叫醒你起身餵佢食早餐","createTime":"2016-11-27T16:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T15:00:57.000Z","uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5add2d8e283abed1a465cc75fb20b62049f5c5d","tid":7072,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"我嗰兩隻衰野 喺餵之前一兩個鐘<br />\n就開始喵喵喵 會用唔同調既叫法<br />\n見你無反應就開始打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再見你無反應就踩上我個頭搞我啲頭髮<br />\n絕招係重覆跳上我個肚到<br />\n個下會覺得自己係條海參想嘔哂自己啲內臟出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無方法可以令佢乖乖地等夠鐘先食早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c852c93d61a048e054d59c7b6fe0ec64f951d13","tid":7072,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"鎖門訓"},{"pid":"f95a20b81c4158e9b8f005589c81adde9c29f60d","tid":7072,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:53:22.000Z","msg":"唔會 因為佢知道點叫我都唔會落床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以會去叫阿媽好過 唔洗晒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97b6541f0cdb6d09e4806c1c1c7af9939ddcc25","tid":7072,"uid":11854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"唔會成日，因為我放一日嘅長糧比佢～無先加～但有時佢食哂我又無加到佢就會嘈到痴左線咁～同埋佢會食得好急之後易嘔先放一日長糧～"},{"pid":"390e94aba09e509b36d014dd37ebe104e506f014","tid":7072,"uid":29703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:22:49.000Z","msg":"唔會，佢會出大廳開始纏住我，等我著好鞋拎好野，同我行到大門口，佢轉入廚房食早餐，等我自己出門口"},{"pid":"02c38d28d92709e1bb15436eca589a507967f37b","tid":7072,"uid":30079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a7138890fa4f4275973bc825bc73202875e4a7","tid":7072,"uid":10183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"神早流流推鳩我門要我放佢行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ee2ec4e1769ecb5f7c7bc27128da5656dfea82","tid":7072,"uid":33553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:16:39.000Z","msg":"會，一到8點就狂叫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2i9bzH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2i9bzH.jpg&h=a0a594e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27e992741d76280bc7ecb4c5121f892792469bd9","tid":7072,"uid":4725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會 因為佢知道點叫我都唔會落床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以會去叫阿媽好過 唔洗晒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98bf30bdcfddc2e88a6bb1262883790197e6f05","tid":7072,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:26:43.000Z","msg":"唔會，等到我起身出廳佢先會跟住我喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68c9330a57a8bc96a92823ca39671660d1fca53","tid":7072,"uid":5176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:11:53.000Z","msg":"會，仲會咬鳩我腳指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我收埋啲腳指就咬我個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f8c1b4c59ba19ca7dfdf1f5d2a19fc16b40560","tid":7072,"uid":1205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會，一到8點就狂叫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/2i9bzH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2i9bzH.jpg&h=267e687d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個樣好愁"},{"pid":"2802ae3d9c4e5f4932de33680c23987b9dad8ebe","tid":7072,"uid":28277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}